---
title: Gambas Pil Pil-Inspired Bowls with Arugula and Feta Side Salad
description: Our juicy shrimp is the star of the show here. Fried in garlic butter and seasoned with smoked paprika, they're served up with colourful roasted veg and a peppery arugula side salad. They need nothing more than a finishing squeeze of lemon.
